snippet.title: WarSphere // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2451530/WarSphere/

WarSphere is a fast-paced, roguelike top-down shooter. As a spherical death robot, you blast, dash and loot your way through procedurally generated worlds. It's all about the pew pew.

Developed by 
Last Tuesday Games
